subsection.def:
Chairperson (主席) includes a
                person appointed to act as Chairperson under section 4 of the
                    Schedule to the Ordinance;

identity card (身分證) means
                an identity card within the meaning of section 1A of the Registration of
                Persons Ordinance (Cap. 177);

review (覆核), in relation to a
                guardianship order, means a review under section 59U(2) or (3) of the
                Ordinance of the order;

paragraph.text:
it is necessary in the interests of the welfare of the mentally incapacitated
                    person or for the protection of other persons that the mentally incapacitated
                    person should be so received;
